description: Use this api to get transit warehouse list which is specific first mile tracking number generation for carrier delivery method

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: This is to indicate the timestamp of the request. Required for all requests. Expires in 5 minutes.

parameters.name: access_token
parameters.description: The token for API access, valid in one day - obtain value for multiple use and expires in 4 hours

parameters.name: shop_id
parameters.description: Shopee's unique identifier for a shop. Required param for most APIs

parameters.name: sign
parameters.description: Signature generated to prevent API call from being tampered

parameters.name: region
parameters.description: Two-character country code indicating the region you want to ship panel. Available value: CN

response_fields.name: error
response_fields.description: Error error type if error happens

response_fields.name: message
response_fields.description: Indicate error type if error happens

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for an API request for error tracking

response_fields.name: warehouse_name_en
response_fields.description: The name of transit warehouse in English

response_fields.name: warehouse_name_cn
response_fields.description: The name of transit warehouse in Chinese
